::KitKat::

"Not much to tell. Megatron is the leader of our pack. There are is a 
mouse who runs the computer. You'll like her. Quickstrike has a girl 
named Stringtra. She's a nice girl.  There a few bots however that 
I'd keep a sharp eye out for.  They are brothers. They talk a good 
fight, but it's all talk so as I've seen." She didn't want to put to 
much info out for this new wolf.  He may have been a friend of 
QUickstrike's, but she was still a little wary of the newcomer.
